= David A. Granger (·) = Mntucing hngkawas 1945 idas 7 jiyax 15 ka David A. Granger ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bukung klwaan Guyana ta sayang o kiya ka David A. Granger, pnaah hngkawas 2015 idas 5 jiyax 16 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
= David A. Granger (·) = David Arthur Granger (Kari Ingkoku: David Arthur Granger, kngkawas 1945 idas 7 diyax 15-), snaw, Guyana, mnsoto Guyana.
